160000051.name: Luna Crystal

The tradability of the pet born from the Luna Crystal follows the tradability of the base pet. 
The Luna Crystal rewards are replaced once every set period. (The list of obtainable items and rates can be viewed from the Cash Shop Updates or the Random Box Rates page on the website.)
